February 28, 1997

To: Deborah Donovan; wluk@ansi.org

Name:      Dietmar Kuehl
Company:   Universitdt Konstanz 
Address:   Fakultdt f|r Mathematik und Informatik
           Postfach 5560/D188
	   D-78434 Konstanz 
